        "markdown": "# Bootstrap Tutorial\n\nThis file now acts as a compatibility entry.\n\nThe canonical lesson is **Bootstrap Your LLM**.\n\nUse it when you want the full declaration-first handshake, the current primitive vocabulary, and the example JSON shape that Twilite expects today."
      }
    },
