      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-bootstrap-compat"
        },
        "markdown": "## What To Do\n\n1. Open **Bootstrap Your LLM** for the real lesson.\n2. Open the onboarding contract if you need the prose version.\n3. Return to **Start Here** if you want the larger tutorial map.\n\nThis graph stays here so older links still land somewhere truthful."
      }
    },
